title: Taggart Episodes 50-56
description:
This is the 3rd third of a set of Hard to Find Taggart Episodes between 
Mark McManus and Alex Norton. Since there are several differences 
on the internet as to which season the episodes fall into...........
I shall number them as episodes aired from the start of TAGGART 
and not use the season they fell into.


E50 Wavelength

E51 Football Crazy

E52 Falling in Love

E53 Death Trap

E54 Fire-Burn

E55 Watertight

E56 The Friday Event
